            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>remaining chopped onion</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until softened</p>\n<p>Drain and rinse the <strong>black beans</strong></p>",
